      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3164_0005"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb41240"><foreign xml:lang="fra">Autriche</foreign></rs>.</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Herrn</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168934">IX. Frankga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>se 1</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="center"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3164_0006"/><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb182">Paris</rs></hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>23. 1. 94</date></dateline></opener><p>Sofort – ehe es <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02607-1"/>verboten<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L02607-1">Zu Kritik an <rs type="person" ref="#pmb64866">Niemanns</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="work" ref="#pmb79030">Der
                     Junggesell</rs> siehe etwa <bibl><rs type="person" ref="#pmb88276">Adolf Silberstein</rs>: <rs type="work" ref="#pmb88273">Heirathen oder nicht?</rs> In: <rs type="work" ref="#pmb52212">Pester Lloyd</rs>, Nr. 151, <date>23. 6. 1894</date>,
                     S. [3–4]</bibl>.</note> wird – kommen la<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en: <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb64866">August Niemann</rs></hi>: <rs type="work" ref="#pmb79030">Der Jungge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ell</rs>. <rs type="place" ref="#pmb168">Berlin</rs>, <rs type="org" ref="#pmb87782">Philo<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ophi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ch-Hi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tori<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>cher Verlag</rs>, <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb87783">Dr. R. Salinger</rs></hi>, <date>1894</date>.</p><closer>Grüße,<lb/><signed>Paul Goldmann.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
